    "◁Other new pieces of notation will be introduced as we go.2 From Partial-State Frames to Possibility Frames Partial-State Frames and SemanticsWe take the following structures as our starting point for the semantics of normal modal logics.Definition 2.1 (Partial-State Frames and Models).",
